{"id": "art-20293", "label": "Art. 20293", "title": "Art. 20293: Obligaţiile mandatarului", "slug": "art-20293", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1803805030\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1077\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1803805030\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 2029<sup>3</sup>:\nObliga&#355;iile mandatarului </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1300522682\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1076\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1300522682\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>În vederea asigur&#259;rii bun&#259;st&#259;rii morale\n&#351;i materiale a mandantului, orice decizie referitoare la executarea\nmandatului este luat&#259; în interesul mandantului &#351;i asigur&#259;\nrespectarea demnit&#259;&#355;ii, a drepturilor &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;ilor\nacestuia, a voin&#355;ei, nevoilor &#351;i preferin&#355;elor lui, precum\n&#351;i salvgardarea autonomiei sale. Dispozi&#355;iile art. 174 alin. (1)\n&#351;i (2) se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor &#351;i mandatarului.</span></p>"}